1.title: En cuerpo ajeno
1.plot: After a one-night relationship with a new girl, the playboy Lalo Padilla is condemned to suffer the effects of a spell cast by that vengeful woman: Lalo has become Lola and must now live as a woman who works in a publishing House.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: Natalia causes Sole's resignation. Aguirre realizes how much he needs Sole working in High Five so he tells his daughter off. Sole finds herself lonely and disappointed while Lola tries to state clearly that she doesn't want anything to do with Facundo.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Lola feels some attraction towards Facundo while at his apartment. Meanwhile, Sole plans to meet a man she's known on the Internet (Mario), but he happens to be Pato, although he doesn't know Sole is his new conquest.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: Gastón finds a new way to expose Lola: he forces her to undergo a medical revision alleging working issues. Secretly, he has made sure that terrible results will crop up from the tests as he has paid the doctor to do so.

imdb.plot outline: Lalo Padilla is a magazine editor and a womanizer who doesn't know what love means, he always underestimate women until his last girlfriend casted a spell on the night of an eclipse that changed his life forever. Lalo wakes up in the body of a beautiful woman not knowing what to do, how it happened or how to reverse it! However until he figures all this out he has to deal with the situation - all with the help of his best friend Grace he manages to convince every one that he is Lola Padilla cousin of Lalo Padilla, she experiences the true love for the first time and the full effects of being a woman and in particular how women are treated by men.
imdb.title: Lalola
plot: A man transforms to a very beautiful woman on the night of an eclipse, falls in love for the first time with another man who doesn't know who she was before.::lovelyaltagracia
